data.description: Great 3 Bedroom/ 2 Bath, well cared for home! A third bedroom was converted for use as a Dining Room but will be changed back for the 3rd bedroom prior to closing. There is an upper level but only 2 steps. Formal Living Room and Dining Room/Den with Fireplace, complete with gas logs. Kitchen has newer appliances and granite countertops! Spacious Sunroom for entertaining that has access to a huge Deck. Downstairs has a large Bonus Room area that might be converted to 2 additional Bedrooms. It currently has a lift installed on the stairway. Laundry/storage room is on this level and, again, could easily have a Bathroom added. Attached 2 car garage with door opener and keypad entry. Huge, well manicured lawn. Home is on septic but public sewer is available. Home sold as is. Convenient to shopping, dining and medical as well as the mountains and lakes of South Carolina. Call today! This home conveys with just the lot it is located on, not the complete tract as recorded.
